channel.title: Server Resource Leak?
channel.description:
What if my Eclipse warns me that there are resource leaks in my server source?
And whenever I run the server I start to lag and eventually crash. I believe it's the cause.

item.title: Server Resource Leak?
item.dc:creator: @xx_matty_xx Justin Bieber
item.description:
@xx_matty_xx wrote:

It depends on the code that the warning is for. It will tell you the line numbers.

It usually means that you have an IO object that isn’t getting closed, but sometimes the warnings are incorrect.

Read full topic
